===on OSX, docker port 2375 refused error:
https://github.com/sequenceiq/docker-socat
which says run $(docker run sequenceiq/socat)
dont forget to change
docker {
      useApi=true
      maintainer = 'Magnus Larsson <magnus.larsson.ml@gmail.com>'
      baseImage = 'java:8'
      hostUrl='http://docker:2375'
  }

ip address should be correct docker address!is



===on EC2 linux, docker port 2375 refused error:

$ sudo <path to>/docker -H 0.0.0.0:2375 -d &


===/etc/hosts add docker to known hosts

