===test deployment on vitural box ubuntu server
ssh timed out?
configure in virtualbox settings -> network -> portforwarding, set:
host ip: 127.0.0.1    host port: 2222    guest ip: [ifconfig in ubuntu image]   guest port: 22
then in ur mac, type ssh tsa45@localhost -p 2222